Jeremy Gittins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremy_Gittins 0 Philip Jeremy Gittins (born 30 January 1956) is an English actor who is known for his role as the Vicar in the highly successful BBC sitcom Keeping Up Appearances from 1990 to 1995.
